00:59:14,546 --> 00:59:16,546
If not on watch, stand down.

616
00:59:17,671 --> 00:59:18,880
Guys...

617
00:59:19,546 --> 00:59:21,838
Now or never for a workout or shower.

618
00:59:22,005 --> 00:59:23,088
Or even both.

619
