01:02:21,921 --> 01:02:24,380
<i>Two incoming messages for CO and XO.</i>

662
01:02:24,546 --> 01:02:26,671
<i>Superencrypted messages.</i>

663
01:02:34,671 --> 01:02:36,130
On my way for decryption.

664
